title: Discokitten Iphone
description:
Awesome, unique gameplay. You've never played anything like it!

You play as Punka, the rhythmic robo-kitten whose job it is to collect energy from canisters to feed Bunka, the giant, hungry head.

Energy is the name of the game here and Disco Kitten has it to spare! Use your quick-firing fingers to teleport Punka around the platforms draining the energy from each canister while avoiding the lightning from above. Are your reflexes quick enough?

Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ RHYTHMIC
Increase your score by stringing together speedy combos and triggering Disco Time. In Disco Time the canisters drain quicker giving you more energy in less time!
